Subject: Red Hat Ethical Hacking Competition
Description: Red Hat has brought great content to Penguicon once again!  Ethical hacking is testing the IT resources for a good cause and for the betterment of technology. This event will provide an opportunity for both novices and experts to brush up on their skills and compete for prizes. Noteworthy Addendum! There will be 20 laptops available in the lab. First come, first served.  Speakers include:Tom Callahan - Track: Tech  - Duration: 2 hours and 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none
